Leonidas invited to the gladiator arena
Not only the gladiators stood ankle-deep in the mud at the first Rheinbacher Römertag in the amusement park.
But the attraction of the event was strong enough to attract well over 1000 visitors yesterday, who braved the rain showers and the autumn cold and were completely inspired by the historical spectacle.
